    <title type="html"><![CDATA[ls命令行排序]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.newtomato.me/blog/lsming-ling-xing-pai-xu.html/"/>
    <updated>2015-10-17T22:26:44+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.newtomato.me/blog/lsming-ling-xing-pai-xu</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="section">按文件大小降序排列</h2>
<blockquote>
  <p>ls -lSr </p>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="section-1">查看当前电脑上硬盘的使用情况</h2>
<blockquote>
  <p>df -lh</p>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="m">这是按兆（M）来排序</h2>
<blockquote>
  <table>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>du -sh *</td>
        <td>sort -rm</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="section-2">选出排在前面的10个</h2>
<blockquote>
  <table>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>du -sh *</td>
        <td>sort -rm</td>
        <td>head</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="section-3">选出排在后面的10个</h2>
<blockquote>
  <table>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>du -sh *</td>
        <td>sort -rm</td>
        <td>tail</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</blockquote>
